When moving an issue into a new project, there is no notification sent to any stakeholders in the new project. You can set a notification for the original project stakeholders, but it's more critical for the new stakeholders to know they have a new issue to watch. We've found many issues get lost or go unnoticed for a while unless we dig them up with filters when issues are moved around. This is costing us when issues are found hiding later in the cycle.

